Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when i was a kid,\Nin a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,i was gazin' up to\Nthe promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す heart！ beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,i just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wake！ up！ your！ heart！ beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,brave and boiling heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を示せ high！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,over boost！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is a real deal！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no more liars
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ignition's on, my heart is on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fire fire fire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.97,0:01:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动 燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动 燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.33,0:01:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…And so, we met in the deep\Ndark and shattered place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no one will come to us. They\Nleft us here with disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we all abanded sadness.\NWe all abanded kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the world is full of hatred.\NThere's no hope, then take this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘で建った塔の　深層で燃える炎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（早々気を付けろ背後）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,be ready. Burn up！ liars！\Nin this cold night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただで消え去る罪など無い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,oh baby, cry out louder\Nto this bad luck
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,god, hear the scream,\Nshare us your light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tonight, now stand up and head\Nup cause we're falling up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（who is the bloody liar？\Nyou all the bloody liar）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創傷疼いている　何故痛いくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah 今疼き出す…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is what's behind the truth.\NWe know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is what's behind the truth.\NWe know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们相遇在这个深幽破碎之境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会来 他们把我们留在这蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:21:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是孤独的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀遗弃了我们 仁慈遗弃了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界充满着憎恶 没有希望 执此前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用谎言树立的塔 在其深处燃烧的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（随时小心身后）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准备 燃烧吧骗子！在这冰冷的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.19,0:22:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪必须付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 宝贝 为你的厄运大声哭喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 请聆听这哭号 赐下您的圣光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜 匍匐跌倒之人请起身抬头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（谁是可恶的骗子？你们全是可恶的骗子）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创伤在隐隐作痛 为何如此痛彻心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 此刻疼痛再起...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是大人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 黄金！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你不能原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 成功了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 王舞在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金..酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等..又..讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方知不知羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱是世界通用的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这 这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 毕竟东酱一直都待在国外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的年轻人真是没规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国外长大的就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是对他网开一面如何？木乃亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喂 我才不是在保护你”它说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 但是道谢总是要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答我一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器是生物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还要废话到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩骨头了啊 这个情况不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干干瘪瘪 营养不足吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可没法去见母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的舞武器拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你把心脏拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏怎么能拱手让人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别贫嘴 废话少说快拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你更会使用心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的心脏 你却更会使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧你？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 你在戏弄我么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊君 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说的根本不是同一件事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为东酱他好像连舞武器是什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 也拥有类似这样的东西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 我就知道是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是心脏之人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能撤退了 好不容易来到这里的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 错过这次机会就没有下回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你掉至地面至今已过十年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为一直待在海外就能装成一无所知的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什么都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器也是今天第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 柊君！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器会因主人的危机而做出反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掩着藏着 亮出来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 柊君和东酱怎能起打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你那一股子臊气的拳头能打倒我么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为帮老爸报了仇 很开心么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的闹剧一定让你觉得挺自豪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手酱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次睁大眼睛瞧着吧 心爱的右手酱的死状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 站着都吃力的小鬼么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 东酱快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲是破坏世界的罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的罪孽由你来偿还吧 用你的这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只宠物 调教得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊 它要在这里和主人说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 要做还是做得到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手酱？右手酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..我认识那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是过去让上野化为火海的家伙的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 一群杂鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你们的熊样 礼央子的走狗们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 不准你用母亲的王舞做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫柊对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你叫东是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这个当心脏的太不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只好自由发挥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 我倒也更喜欢一直自由自在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要..有当心脏的样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 果然来得够快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 刚才问我为什么要做这种事对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告诉你那个理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是为了引出那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的..舞乱伎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了啊 万流礼央子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:11:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 汀的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}第二话 炎之巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 把炎帝击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明礼央子的邪恶本质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎帝在24年前的战斗中失去了手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它应该发挥不出原本的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 看这样有戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子 明明同为舞武器使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却背叛了舞武器使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的背叛 其他舞武器使全被当成了反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是真正的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你 让我的父亲发了疯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你夺走了父亲身为舞武器使的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要夺回父亲的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来摧毁你建立起的统治体制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来夺回被你葬送的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来..由我来..由我来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说真相？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要把所谓的真相..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和只剩骨头的舞乱伎一起从坟墓里挖出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就把你们和王舞一起化为枯骨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们的五脏六腑彻底沸腾 蒸发殆尽吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那帮小鬼们 这下肯定活不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这明明不是原本的力量啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一希汀犯下的罪孽 永远都不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊？为什么认识我的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长着一双和我最讨厌的女人一样的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我恶心的想吐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到黄金他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来怎么办？队长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊 别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们乖乖按照我的指示办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的王舞就不会输给炎帝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理 你的意思是我们的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错啊 是你们拖了我的后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮没用的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 别对舞武器撒气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？它们不过是道具而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不会说话也没有痛觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿你的屁股代替它们让我踢几脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 来试试看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柊君 木乃酱 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是我们吵架的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我会罢手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过得让我先揍这家伙一拳再说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎帝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汀的儿子 有个好消息告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从漂浮在空中的舞乱伎巢穴中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一台舞乱伎坠落地面 这可是十年来从未有过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这十年来一直在防止舞乱伎坠落地面的你的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一希汀的生命已经走到尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一希汀她..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让汀一个人上路太孤单了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你马上去追随她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的火力 这下看来没戏唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正要死的话 至少把我烤成可口的样子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间就会化成灰烬啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 事情变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有找你来的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 黄金酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她死了的话 坠落的舞乱伎应该不止一台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人都把我的母亲称为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是母亲不是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲现在也孤身一人在宝岛努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保护这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次轮到我用王舞登上宝岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来保护母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不像马上要被烧死之人的台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱 还有各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们从没有把我的母亲称为魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让我很开心 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞武器 舞乱伎的手足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是它的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们的力量借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们的舞武器托付给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托付给担当心脏的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 我..我..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 做女人要干脆 应下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是朋友的请求..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要帮你这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 男人别啰哩啰嗦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢敌视我万流礼央子和炎帝的一希之血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只消将其斩草除根！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全敌不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量完全不起作用么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 五个人各自行动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一个人都战胜不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 大家齐心协力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别喊得那么得瑟！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 要飞咯 右手酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用炎帝去扫荡坠落地面的舞乱伎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备好列车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请问小鬼们怎么处置？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他们 等我处理掉坠落的舞乱伎之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再将他们连同一希汀一起除掉便是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人？礼央子大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了心脏之舞武器的一希血脉么..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 前辈 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但王舞逃之夭夭 连舞武器使的小鬼们都给溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:22:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你礼央子大人的情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都没有变化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人的时间依然是停滞不前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和24年前一样 保持着16岁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.54,0:23:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不等礼央子大人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去召集其他的四天王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但王舞被偷 还有舞乱伎坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事情要变得有趣起来了啊